column1: #Text=Toronto Comicon 2019 welcomes fans with celebrities , creativity , cosplay
#Text=Toronto Comicon 2019 returned to its titular city from March 15 to 17 , as one of the largest pop culture events in Canada .

#Text=The popular event featured celebrity guests like actors Dan Fogler , Ron Perlman , John De Lancie , John Rhys-Davies , and Jaleel White , as well as comic artists , authors , and professional cosplayers .
#Text=The event included a large show floor with hundreds of retailers and artists promoting their creations .
#Text=Wikinews ' Nicholas Moreau attended the event , taking photos of the various sights .
#Text=John Rhys-Davies broke news when he revealed that a Sliders reboot is being considered .
#Text=" Jerry [ O'Connell ] and I are talking to NBC at the moment .

column1: #Text=Special effects costumer Ian Campbell , whose screen credits include Star Trek : Discovery , had a booth at the convention displaying his prop replicas and cosplay items .
#Text=Amidst the bustle of activity , Campbell was working on a Thanos helmet sculpt .

#Text=After the convention , he told Wikinews that " it can be tough to maintain focus with so many people streaming past and along questions , but sculpting in front of a crowd at conventions is great because it allows people to see the process that goes into what I do [ ... ]

#Text=Mancini told Wikinews after the event that the best part of cosplay is  bringing a character to life . "

column1: #Text=One of the characters she took on this year was Squirrel Girl , a Marvel Comics character .
#Text=Mancini has been described by the Daily Hive as a " squirrel whisperer " , for the close affinity some of the animals have for her .
#Text=Stephanie Chapman as Abe Sapien from Hellboy .
#Text=Stephanie Chapman has knit a variety of knit outfits , an uncommon technique for cosplay .
#Text=Prompted by Ron Perlman 's visit , she wore a costume based on Hellboy character Abe Sapien , which lacks the eyeholes of her normal masks .
#Text=With " Abe , I wanted to go for accuracy over comfort , " Chapman told Wikinews , a choice leaving her largely helpless without a handler .
#Text=The costume " is very warm [ ... ] so I have to stay hydrated and try to keep as calm as possible .
